Assignment: Create Console Application using .NET Framework and .NET Core and Analyze the Bin Folder

Aim:
To create Console Applications using .NET Framework and .NET Core, analyze the bin folder contents, and view assembly metadata using ILDASM.

.NET Framework Console Application

using System;

class Program
{
    static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        Console.WriteLine("Hello from .NET Framework");
        Console.ReadLine();
    }
}

.NET Core Console Application

using System;

namespace DotNetCoreApp
{
    class Program
    {
        static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            Console.WriteLine("Hello from .NET Core");
        }
    }
}

